<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->
  <meta name="description" content="">
  <meta name="author" content="">
  <link rel="icon" href="../../favicon.ico">

  <title>Backyard Lion International</title>
</head>

<body>
<div class="table-responsive">
  <table class="table">
    <!-- coverphoto -->
    <%= image_tag("europe-hero.jpg", class: "background-cover-head dj") %>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
<div class="container">
  <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-premium" style="border:none !important;">
    <h1 style="color: #367cb8;">Sports
      <small> continue your career, make money, experience the world</small>
    </h1><br>
    <p>Have you ever thought of using the sport you love to EXPLORE THE WORLD? Now you can. Backyard Lion connects
      you with sport teams all over the world so you can make authentic life experiences -- coach or play.</p>
    <br>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="border-form-div">
        <div class="form-signin">
          <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
              <%= devise_error_messages! %>
              <h2 class="form-signin-heading">Sign up</h2>
              <%= f.text_field :first_name, class: "form-control", placeholder: "First Name",
                               :style => 'margin-bottom: -1px; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;' %>
              <%= f.text_field :last_name, placeholder: "Last Name", :class => 'form-control',
                               :style => 'margin-bottom: -1px; border-top-left-radius: 0; border-top-right-radius: 0; border-radius: 0px;' %>
              <%= f.email_field :email, :placeholder => 'Email address', :class => 'form-control',
                                :style => 'margin-bottom: -1px; border-top-left-radius: 0; border-top-right-radius: 0; border-radius: 0px;' %>
              <%= f.password_field :password, :placeholder => 'Password', :class => 'form-control', :style => 'margin-bottom: -1px; border-top-left-radius: 0; border-top-right-radius: 0; border-radius: 0px;' %>
              <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :placeholder => 'Password confirmation', :class => 'form-control' %>
              <div class="checkbox">
                <label>
                  <input type="checkbox" value="remember-me"> Remember me
                </label>
              </div>
              <label class="radio-inline">
                <%= f.radio_button(:user_type, "athlete") %> Athlete or Coach
              </label>
              <label class="radio-inline">
                <%= f.radio_button(:user_type, "team") %> Team
              </label><br/>
              <%= f.submit "Sign up", :class => 'btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block', :style => 'margin-top: 10px;' %>
          <% end %>
          <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<!-- How it works text -->
<div class="page-header">
  <h1 class='primary-color text-center'>How it works
    <small> three simple steps</small>
  </h1>
</div>


<div class="container">
  <!-- Example row of columns -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <a class="thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag("discover-amazing-locations.jpg") %>
      </a>
      <h2 class="primary-color"><span class="steps-badge" style="display:inline;">1</span> Discover
        <small> amazing locations</small>
      </h2>
      <p>Whether an opportunity in Paris, Rome, or Barcelona, Backyard Lion connects athletes to unique travel and
        playing experiences.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <a class="thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag("hero-image0.png") %>
      </a>
      <h2 class="primary-color"><span class="steps-badge" style="display:inline;">2</span> Connect
        <small> with a team</small>
      </h2>
      <p>With over 1,500 world-class teams all over the world and a growing community of users, Backyard Lion is the easiest way for people
        to connect to real-life opportunities overseas. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <a class="thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag("go-play-aboard.jpg") %>
      </a>
      <h2 class="primary-color"><span class="steps-badge" style="display:inline;">3</span> Go
        <small> play abroad</small>
      </h2>
      <p>Experience all a foreign culture has to offer, continue your career and make money at the same time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="jumbotron-image">
</div>

<h1 class="primary-color text-center">Play Abroad
  <small> do you want to see your opportunities?</small>
</h1>
  <br>
  <p class="text-center"><%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></p>

<hr>

<footer style="padding: 20px;">
  <p>&copy; 2016 Backyard Lion
    <small>International</small>
    , LLC
  </p>
  <p>Backyard Lion is a trusted community marketplace for sport people to list, discover, and connect with unique
    opportunites around the world â€” online desktop or from a mobile phone.</p>
</footer>
</div> <!-- /container -->
</body>
</html>



















    